title: Black & Decker The Complete Guide to Decks (2012) Gooner
description:
Black & Decker The Complete Guide to Decks - Plan & Build Your Dream Deck Includes Complete Deck Plans - Updated 5th Edition (2012) (Pdf & Epub) Gooner

Publisher: Cool Springs Press; 5 edition (January 1, 2012)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1589236599
ISBN-13: 978-1589236592

The most detailed, most current and most complete deck building book on the market. It reflects the latest changes in building codes and it features deck building materials that are popular today. The additional two signatures (32 pages) contain all-new deck plans with complete plan drawings. Updates to the materials section focus on new composite and non-wood deck building alternatives, as well as the current generation of deck hardware that resists corrosion caused by non-CCA pressure treated lumber. Step-by-step projects feature clever ways to customize and accessorize your deck to enhance both utility and enjoyment
